description:
Veteran nightlife mainstays Brian Vidal & Holodec have been steadily providing dancers with their signature blend of house, garage, breaks and the spectrum of dance music at parties big and small, from clubs to warehouses. Join them every month on NTS Radio for a back2back set broadcast live from our LA studio.
